@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zenilj(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.sin(v0 + 0.07) - (v2 + 0.81 * v2 + 0.43)))
    v1 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.94) * (v2 + 0.51 / v2 + 1.00)) / v0)
    v1 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.32 / v0 + 0.55)) * wp.cos(tmp))
    tmp = (0.36 - 0.58)
    v2 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
